&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting for highly motivated, skilled Registered Nurses of all disciplines to work as a lead nurse in the Continuing Care team in Bradford districts CCG on a fixed term basis until March 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must be able to demonstrate knowledge and experience of the CHC legislation and process. Assessment, including risk assessment, and case management skills are essential. You should have excellent communication and interpersonal skills with the ability to produce clear and concise written reports. Full-time and part-time hours considered&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details please contact&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Caroline Parker - Clinical Leads c.healthcare@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
